high_descs: turn around and move to the sink
pick up the knife from the sink
move to the potato in the sink
slice the potato in the sink
drop the knife in the sink
pick up the slice of the potato
turn right and head to the fridge
place the potato to cool and then take it out
turn around and head for the bin
place the potato in the bin
anns.task_desc: place a cold potato slice in the bin

high_descs: Turn left at the door, walk left around the counter and take a right at the stove to reach the sink.
Pick up the knife with the yellow handle from behind the green cup on the left counter.
Look down at the sink.
Slice the potato inside the sink.
Put the knife inside the sink.
Pick up a slice of potato from inside the sink.
Turn right and walk to the fridge on the left.
Put the slice of potato inside the fridge on the top left shelf, chill it, remove it and close the door.
Turn around, hang a right at the wall and walk to the black bin on the floor to the right.
Put the chilled slice of potato inside the black bin on the floor.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled slice of potato in a bin.

high_descs: Walk over to the kitchen sink.
Pick up the large metal knife off of the counter to the left of the sink.
Look down at the kitchen sink.
Slice up the potato that is in the kitchen sink.
Put the large metal knife in the kitchen sink.
Pick up a piece of sliced potato out of the sink.
Turn right and walk over to the fridge.
Open the fridge and put the piece of sliced potato inside then close the door, after a couple seconds open the fridge back up and remove the piece of sliced potato then close the door.
Turn around and walk across the room, then hang a right and walk up to the door, turn right to face the counter.
Put the chilled piece of sliced potato in the small black bin on the ground in front of the counter.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled piece of sliced potato in a small back bin.
